"{\"uid\": \"highsnobiety.com-p-jordan-6-olympic-sneakers-2024\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Create an account to share your reaction and engage with the community.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 71, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"By signing up, you agree to Highsnobiety'sPrivacy PolicyandTerms & Conditions.\", \"from\": 73, \"to\": 151, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Already have an account?Sign in  Another reborn classic is back from the Nike vault.\", \"from\": 153, \"to\": 237, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 226, \"end\": 230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"score\": 0.9642940131873755, \"rank\": 0.03702800728481088, \"text\": \"Nike\", \"types\": [\"Q728\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This time, the sportswear brand has dusted off the Air Jordan 6 \\\"Olympic\\\" just in time for the upcoming Paris Games.\", \"from\": 238, \"to\": 354, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Debuted in 2000 for the Sydney Olympics and later revived in 2012, the iconicJordan 6 sneakeris back... and looking as good as ever.\", \"from\": 356, \"to\": 488, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Aside from a minor update to the midsole (it's got new colorblocking!\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 559, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"), the Jordan 6 sneaker remains the Olympic classic we have loved since the aughts.\", \"from\": 559, \"to\": 642, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 566, \"end\": 572, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"score\": 0.9999784661712771, \"rank\": 2.1488331756685334e-05, \"text\": \"Jordan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2024 Air Jordan 6 \\\"Olympic\\\" sneaker arrives with extra crisp leather construction, stroked with those familiar deep navy blue and white shades.\", \"from\": 644, \"to\": 791, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Red bursts top signature details, while more patriotic hues decorate the new midsole alongside icy-like touches (appropriate for such a cold shoe).\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 940, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris Olympics are set to finally kick off in July and wrap up in August.\", \"from\": 942, \"to\": 1019, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"From the looks of it, Nike plans to help close out the Summer Games with a bang - the bang being the Jordan 6's re-release.\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1143, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1042, \"end\": 1046, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"score\": 0.9642940131873755, \"rank\": 0.03702800728481088, \"text\": \"Nike\", \"types\": [\"Q728\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to sneaker leakers, Nike will unleash the Air Jordan 6 \\\"Olympic\\\" sneakers on August 3 atNikeand select retailers.\", \"from\": 1145, \"to\": 1268, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1175, \"end\": 1179, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"score\": 0.9642940131873755, \"rank\": 0.03702800728481088, \"text\": \"Nike\", \"types\": [\"Q728\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These will join a pretty big lineup of Nike Olympic sneaker releases.\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1338, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1308, \"end\": 1312, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"score\": 0.9642940131873755, \"rank\": 0.03702800728481088, \"text\": \"Nike\", \"types\": [\"Q728\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Indeed, Nike has loads of shoes on the roster for the big games, including some stealthyall-grey Jordan 4s, awild Dunk sneaker, andproblem-solving skate shoes.\", \"from\": 1340, \"to\": 1499, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1348, \"end\": 1352, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"score\": 0.9642940131873755, \"rank\": 0.03702800728481088, \"text\": \"Nike\", \"types\": [\"Q728\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\"}, {\"begin\": 1437, \"end\": 1443, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"score\": 0.9999784661712771, \"rank\": 2.1488331756685334e-05, \"text\": \"Jordan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Oh, and thosenice breakdancing shoes, too.\", \"from\": 1501, \"to\": 1543, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Titel Media GmbH (Highsnobiety), is committed to facilitating and improving the accessibility and usability of its Website, www.highsnobiety.com.\", \"from\": 1545, \"to\": 1690, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1545, \"end\": 1550, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Titel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Titel\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Titel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Titel\"}, {\"begin\": 1557, \"end\": 1561, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gesellschaft_mit_beschr\\u00e4nkter_Haftung\", \"score\": 0.9993142668114801, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"GmbH\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gesellschaft_mit_beschr\\u00e4nkter_Haftung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gesellschaft_mit_beschr\\u00e4nkter_Haftung\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Titel Media GmbH strives to ensure that its Website services and content are accessible to persons with disabilities including users of screen reader technology.\", \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 1852, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1691, \"end\": 1696, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Titel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Titel\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Titel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Titel\"}, {\"begin\": 1703, \"end\": 1707, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gesellschaft_mit_beschr\\u00e4nkter_Haftung\", \"score\": 0.9993142668114801, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"GmbH\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gesellschaft_mit_beschr\\u00e4nkter_Haftung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gesellschaft_mit_beschr\\u00e4nkter_Haftung\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To accomplish this, Titel Media GmbH tests, remediates and maintains the Website in-line with the Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG), which also bring the Website into conformance with the Americans with Disabilities Act of 1990.\", \"from\": 1853, \"to\": 2091, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1951, \"end\": 1987, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Web_Content_Accessibility_Guidelines\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Web Content Accessibility Guidelines\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Web_Content_Accessibility_Guidelines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Web_Content_Accessibility_Guidelines\"}, {\"begin\": 1989, \"end\": 1993, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Web_Content_Accessibility_Guidelines\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"WCAG\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Web_Content_Accessibility_Guidelines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Web_Content_Accessibility_Guidelines\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please be aware that our efforts to maintain accessibility and usability are ongoing.\", \"from\": 2093, \"to\": 2178, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While we strive to make the Website as accessible as possible some issues can be encountered by different assistive technology as the range of assistive technology is wide and varied.\", \"from\": 2179, \"to\": 2362, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If, at any time, you have specific questions or concerns about the accessibility of any particular webpage on this Website, please contact us at accessibility@highsnobiety.com, +49 (0)30 235 908 500.\", \"from\": 2364, \"to\": 2563, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you do encounter an accessibility issue, please be sure to specify the web page and nature of the issue in your email and/or phone call, and we will make all reasonable efforts to make that page or the information contained therein accessible for you.\", \"from\": 2564, \"to\": 2818, \"entities\": []}]}"